menu.help:	is time to mount a new form.
menu.help:	
modify.help:ABSTRACT:
modify.help:	[GENERAL]
modify.help:	You use the "modify" task to modify the definition of a
modify.help:	form. The same information you gave when you added the form
modify.help:	will provide the defaults for each item you are asked to
modify.help:	respecify, so you can quickly step through the definition to
modify.help:	find the item you want to modify.
modify.help:	
modify.help:	[Name of form:]
modify.help:	You are expected to enter the name of the form you want to
modify.help:	modify. If you don't know the name, press CHOICES for a
modify.help:	list of known forms.
modify.help:	
modify.help:	[Page length:]
modify.help:	You are expected to enter a number, possibly followed by a
